#N canvas 0 0 1000 900 12;
#X text 40 20 osc-receive.pd --- OSC input for the Shrine sound engine.;
#X text 40 40 Real contract (edge-node firmware + osc-sim/generator.py):;
#X text 40 58 /shrine/node/{0..3} -> 5 floats: self_stdev(=cap presence) carrier_mag(dropped) gsr_mag0 gsr_mag1 gsr_mag2.;
#X text 40 76 node id 0-indexed -> cap-N. The 3 gsr slots map to global pairs via;
#X text 40 94 NODE_GSR_MAPPING = node0:[0 1 2] node1:[3 4 0] node2:[5 1 3] node3:[2 4 5] (see leds/sensor_state.py).;
#X text 40 112 Emits buses cap-0..3 and gsr-mag-0..5 in 0-1. Firmware sends normalized values.;
#X text 40 130 Uses ELSE osc.receive + osc.route. FFT messages caught by first osc.route (reject passes data).;
#X obj 40 180 else/osc.receive 57120;
#X obj 40 220 else/osc.route /shrine/node/0/fft /shrine/node/1/fft /shrine/node/2/fft /shrine/node/3/fft;
#X obj 40 260 else/osc.route /shrine/node;
#X obj 40 300 else/osc.route /0 /1 /2 /3;
